<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Service Voucher</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Great+Vibes&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
    margin:0;
    padding:24px 0;
    font-family: Arial, "Noto Naskh Arabic", "Amiri", Tahoma, sans-serif;
    background:#eef2f7;
    color:#1f2937;
}

.wrapper{
    width:1020px;
    margin:0 auto;
    background:#ffffff;
    padding:24px;
    border:1px solid #dbe3ec;
    border-radius:18px;
    box-shadow:0 14px 40px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);
}

/* HEADER */
.header-table{
    width:100%;
    border-collapse:separate;
    border-spacing:0;
    margin-bottom:18px;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b 55%, #334155);
    border-radius:16px;
    overflow:hidden;
    border:1px solid #1e293b;
}

.header-table td{
    border:none !important;
    vertical-align:middle;
    padding:20px 16px;
    background:transparent !important;
}

.header-table .logo-cell{
    width:22%;
    text-align:center;
}

.header-table .title-cell{
    width:56%;
    text-align:center;
}

.logo-box{
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    background:#ffffff;
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    border-radius:14px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
}

.logo-left-box{
    width:130px;
    height:130px;
    padding:10px;
}

.logo-right-box{
    width:210px;
    height:110px;
    padding:10px 14px;
}

.logo-left{
    max-width:100%;
    max-height:100%;
    width:auto;
    height:auto;
    object-fit:contain;
    display:block;
}

.logo-right{
    max-width:100%;
    max-height:100%;
    width:auto;
    height:auto;
    object-fit:contain;
    display:block;
}

.center-title{
    text-align:center;
    color:#ffffff;
}

.center-title h2{
    margin:0;
    font-size:28px;
    font-weight:800;
    letter-spacing:1px;
    color:#ffffff;
    text-transform:uppercase;
}

.center-title .subline{
    width:90px;
    height:3px;
    background:#fbbf24;
    margin:10px auto 12px;
    border-radius:999px;
}

.center-title p{
    margin:0;
    font-size:12px;
    line-height:1.7;
    color:#dbe4ee;
}

.service-title{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:14px;
    padding:8px 18px;
    border-radius:999px;
    background:rgba(251,191,36,0.14);
    border:1px solid rgba(251,191,36,0.35);
    color:#fbbf24;
    font-size:14px;
    font-weight:700;
    letter-spacing:2.5px;
}

/* GENERIC TABLES */
table{
    width:100%;
    border-collapse:separate;
    border-spacing:0;
    font-size:12px;
    margin-top:10px;
    border:1px solid #d7dee8;
    border-radius:12px;
    overflow:hidden;
}

th, td{
    padding:9px 10px;
    text-align:center;
    border-right:1px solid #d7dee8;
    border-bottom:1px solid #d7dee8;
}

tr:last-child td{
    border-bottom:none;
}

th:last-child, td:last-child{
    border-right:none;
}

th{
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f8fafc,#eef2f7);
    color:#0f172a;
    font-weight:700;
    font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:0.3px;
}

td{
    background:#ffffff;
    color:#1f2937;
}

tr:nth-child(even) td{
    background:#fbfdff;
}

.info-table td{
    font-size:12px;
    padding:10px 10px;
}

.info-table strong{
    color:#111827;
}

.summary-row td{
    background:#f8fafc !important;
    font-weight:700;
    color:#0f172a;
}

.total-row td{
    background:#f8fafc !important;
    font-weight:700;
    color:#0f172a;
}

/* SECTION HEADINGS */
.section-heading{
    margin-top:18px;
    margin-bottom:8px;
    text-align:center;
    font-weight:800;
    letter-spacing:1.8px;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c2d12,#c2410c);
    color:#ffffff;
    padding:10px 14px;
    border-radius:10px;
    font-size:13px;
    box-shadow:0 6px 14px rgba(124,45,18,0.16);
}

/* ALIGNMENT HELPERS */
.center{
    text-align:center;
}

.right{
    text-align:right;
}

/* QR / NOTES AREA */
.qr-wrapper{
    margin-top:14px;
    border-radius:14px;
    overflow:hidden;
}

.qr-wrapper td{
    vertical-align:top;
}

.notes-box{
    text-align:left;
    background:#ffffff;
}

.notes-box strong{
    display:block;
    margin-bottom:8px;
    font-size:13px;
    color:#111827;
}

.notes-box ul{
    margin:0 0 0 18px;
    padding:0;
}

.notes-box li{
    margin-bottom:6px;
    line-height:1.55;
    color:#374151;
}

.qr-card{
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f8fafc,#eef4f9) !important;
    padding:16px 12px;
}

.qr-card img{
    width:145px;
    height:145px;
    object-fit:contain;
    background:#ffffff;
    padding:8px;
    border-radius:12px;
    border:1px solid #d1d5db;
    box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

.qr-card strong{
    display:block;
    font-size:13px;
    line-height:1.6;
    color:#0f172a;
    letter-spacing:0.4px;
}

/* NOTE BOXES */
.note{
    font-size:11.5px;
    margin-top:14px;
    white-space:pre-line;
    background:#fffaf0;
    border:1px solid #f7d68a;
    border-left:5px solid #d97706;
    border-radius:12px;
    padding:14px 16px;
    color:#78350f;
    line-height:1.75;
    box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(217,119,6,0.07);
}

.note strong{
    font-size:12.5px;
}

.arabic-block{
    direction:rtl;
    text-align:right;
    font-size:14px;
    margin-top:12px;
    font-family:"Noto Naskh Arabic","Amiri",Tahoma,Arial,sans-serif;
    background:#ecfdf5;
    border:1px solid #a7f3d0;
    border-right:5px solid #059669;
    border-radius:12px;
    padding:14px 16px;
    color:#065f46;
    line-height:2;
    box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(5,150,105,0.06);
}

.important{
    margin-top:12px;
    font-size:12px;
    color:#7f1d1d;
    background:#fef2f2;
    border:1px solid #fecaca;
    border-left:5px solid #dc2626;
    border-radius:12px;
    padding:14px 16px;
    line-height:1.75;
    box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(220,38,38,0.06);
}

.important strong{
    font-size:12.5px;
    display:block;
    margin-bottom:4px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="wrapper">

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <table class="header-table">
        <tr>
            <td class="logo-cell">
                <% if(company.logo){ %>
                    <div class="logo-box logo-left-box">
                        <img src="<%= company.logo %>" class="logo-left" alt="Company Logo">
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </td>

            <td class="title-cell center-title">
                <h2 style="
                    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
                    font-size: 34px;
                    font-weight: 800;
                    letter-spacing: 4px;
                    word-spacing: 8px;
                    color: red;
                    margin-bottom: 10px;
                ">
                    <%= company.name %>
                </h2>
                <div class="subline"></div>
                <p>
                    <%= company.address %>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Email: <%= company.email %>
                </p>
                <div class="service-title">SERVICE VOUCHER</div>
            </td>

            <td class="logo-cell">
                <% if(foreignCompany.logo){ %>
                    <div class="logo-box logo-right-box">
                        <img src="<%= foreignCompany.logo %>" class="logo-right" alt="Foreign Company Logo">
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- VOUCHER INFO -->
    <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
            <td><strong>UMRAH COMPANY</strong></td>
            <td><%= foreignCompany.name %></td>
            <td><strong>HOTEL VOUCHER#</strong></td>
            <td><%= voucher.voucherNo %></td>
            <td><strong>V-DATE</strong></td>
            <td><%= voucher.date %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><strong>EXECUTIVE AGENT</strong></td>
            <td colspan="5">PKG CATEGORY / DAZ 0%</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- PARTY DETAILS -->
    <div class="section-heading">PARTY DETAILS</div>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>SR</th>
            <th>PAX NAME(S)</th>
            <th>PASSPORT NO.</th>
            <th>GROUP</th>
            <th>VISA NO.</th>
        </tr>

        <% customers.forEach((c,i)=>{ %>
        <tr>
            <td class="center"><%= i+1 %></td>
            <td><%= c.name %></td>
            <td><%= c.passport %></td>
            <td>901052165</td>
            <td><%= c.visaNumber %></td>
        </tr>
        <% }) %>

        <tr class="summary-row">
            <td colspan="5" class="center">
                GENTS: <%= customers.filter(c=>c.gender==='male').length %>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                LADIES: <%= customers.filter(c=>c.gender==='female').length %>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                CHILDREN: <%= customers.filter(c=>c.paxType==='children').length %>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                INFANT: <%= customers.filter(c=>c.paxType==='infant').length %>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                TOTAL PAX: <%= customers.length %>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- ACCOMMODATION -->
    <div class="section-heading">ACCOMMODATION DETAILS</div>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>CITY</th>
            <th>HOTEL NAME</th>
            <th>ROOM</th>
            <th>ROOM TYPE</th>
            <th>CHECK IN</th>
            <th>CHECK OUT</th>
            <th>NIGHTS</th>
        </tr>

        <% hotels.forEach(h=>{ %>
        <tr>
            <td><%= h.city %></td>
            <td><%= h.name %></td>
            <td class="center">1</td>
            <td><%= h.roomType %></td>
            <td><%= h.checkIn %></td>
            <td><%= h.checkOut %></td>
            <td class="center"><%= h.nights %></td>
        </tr>
        <% }) %>

        <tr class="total-row">
            <td colspan="6" class="right"><strong>Total Nights</strong></td>
            <td class="center"><%= hotels.reduce((sum,h)=>sum+h.nights,0) %></td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- TRANSPORT -->
    <div class="section-heading">TRANSPORTATION DETAILS</div>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>TYPE</th>
            <th>ROUTE</th>
        </tr>

        <% transports.forEach(t=>{ %>
        <tr>
            <td><%= t.type %></td>
            <td><%= t.route %></td>
        </tr>
        <% }) %>
    </table>

    <!-- FLIGHT DETAILS -->
    <div class="section-heading">FLIGHT DETAILS</div>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>FLIGHT</th>
            <th>FROM</th>
            <th>TO</th>
            <th>DEPARTURE</th>
            <th>ARRIVAL</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><%= departureFlight.flightNo %></td>
            <td><%= departureFlight.fromCity %></td>
            <td><%= departureFlight.toCity %></td>
            <td><%= departureFlight.date %> - <%= departureFlight.takeoff %></td>
            <td><%= departureFlight.date %> - <%= departureFlight.landing %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><%= arrivalFlight.flightNo %></td>
            <td><%= arrivalFlight.fromCity %></td>
            <td><%= arrivalFlight.toCity %></td>
            <td><%= arrivalFlight.date %> - <%= arrivalFlight.takeoff %></td>
            <td><%= arrivalFlight.date %> - <%= arrivalFlight.landing %></td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- QR + CONTACT -->
    <table class="qr-wrapper">
        <tr>
            <td width="50%" class="notes-box">
                <strong>Notes</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>MAKKAH HOTEL: Uzair 0548335007 (Day) Tariq 0549306332 (Night)</li>
                    <li>MEDINAH HOTEL: MR. ARSALAN +966544809146</li>
                    <li>Transport Contact: +966500000000</li>

                    <% if (notes) { %>
                        <% notes.split('\n').forEach(n => { %>
                            <li><%= n %></li>
                        <% }) %>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
            </td>
            <td width="25%" class="verified-cell">
                <img src="/images/verified2.png" alt="Verified" style="width: 80%;">
            </td>

            <td width="25%" class="center qr-card qr-cell">
                <img src="<%= qrImage %>" alt="QR Code">
                <strong>AUTHORIZED<br><%= company.name.toUpperCase() %></strong>
            </td>
            <style>
                .verified-cell,
                .qr-cell{
                    border: none !important;
                    background: transparent !important;
                }
            </style>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- NOTES -->
    <div class="note">
<strong>Note:</strong><br>
- Please contact Makkah/Madinah operations 24 hours before the scheduled transportation and notify them accordingly.
- Room sharing means 4-6 beds per room.
- Separate room will incur extra cost.
- If the above mentioned hotel is unavailable in that case a similar category hotel will be provided.
- In case of any transport related delays, our esteemed passengers are advised to observe patience at airports and hotels.
- Each and every Pax has to wear wrist band or company badge. If anybody fails to follow directions SAR 2,000 will be charged as penalty per Pax.
- Please when you call for requesting Transportation or any services you must give us the Name of the Agency and the Serial Number above.
- No service will be provided if the vendor fails to notify us the agency name and the serial number.
    </div>

    <!-- ARABIC BLOCK -->
    <div class="arabic-block">
        تنبيه هام: يمنع تسليم جواز السفر لأي شخص داخل المملكة العربية السعودية سواء وكيل أو شركة نقل.
        يرجى التواصل مع وكيل السفر الباكستاني في حال حدوث أي مشكلة.
    </div>

    <div class="important">
        <strong>IMPORTANT NOTICE:</strong>
        Passengers are requested not to hand over their passport to anyone in Saudi Arabia, whether agent or transport provider.
    </div>

    <br/>

    <p id="pageUrl" style="text-decoration: underline; word-break: break-word; font-size: 11px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; color: #666; margin-top: 8px;"></p>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('pageUrl').textContent = window.location.href;
    </script>

</div>

</body>

